OL,3,GNorthern Ireland
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FIt will be a
OL,6,Fdry evening with cloud breaking up to
OL,7,Fgive some late sunny spells. Remaining
OL,8,Fdry overnight with clear spells and
OL,9,Flight winds. Frost in places.
OL,10,
OL,11,CMonday:FA few mist and fog patches
OL,12,Fwhich will be quick to clear in the
OL,13,Fmorning to leave a dry and settled day
OL,14,Fwith light winds and plenty sunny
OL,15,Fspells.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
